title: Thunder are back and the Western Conference is loaded again
text:
> Oklahoma Thunder are back and the Western Conference is loaded again Oklahoma City Thunder forward Kevin Durant points after hitting a 3-pointer during the second half of an NBA preseason basketball game against the Utah Jazz on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, in Salt Lake City.
